subject: everything lana condor eats in a day
body: i'm thankful for lana condor's "[everything i eat in a day](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MY-QS-8Rimk)" video because i already liked her because of her performances and then to find that she likes many of the same things i do and does so exuberantly was a treat.
